Program: Letter from America by Alistair Cooke
Title: Fishing for votes
Link: https://www.bbc.co.uk/programmes/b043xf0v
Last Broadcast Date: Sun 5 Aug 1984
When being poor at sports can help a man who's fishing for votes. This archive edition of Letter from America was recorded by one of two listeners, who between them taped and labelled over 650 Letter From America programmes from 1973 to 1989. It was restored by the BBC in 2014.